column5: Well, maybe not you, but some of you...  Mike's Pics is a wopping 348 points clear of second place - wow....  Approx 300 points seperate second from 15th.  Everyone past 15th has some ground to make up fast if they want to get into contention.  Pretty much every Sens fan is near the bottom and basically out of it - which is totally shocking...  The battle of the Pylons is heating up.  Puckhead's Pylons (13th) had a comfortable lead over Kennymans Pylons (11th) for a good stretch and all of a sudden Kennyman's Pylons have inched ahead by a good 33 points...  Damn.  The Pylon war will be bitter and decisive, sure to go down to the last game.  Plenty of time left to get into the top tier - even for you Sens fans... I picked up almost 310 points the other night.
Wings have it in the bag...
AMEN BROTHER!  But what am I going to do with my 3 trades???   I will start the bidding at $5.00
Agreed. He has done be well so far (8 pts), but gonna pick up Holmstrom to complete the line!  Hopefully Holmstrom will turn it up a notch.
